secretary whose sexual encounter with Bakker toppled his PTL
ministry. She helped state investigators put together the case
agaist her former boss after being promised immunity from
prosecution. She has said she also had an affair with Profeta.
   Profeta admitted in his plea bargain that he tried to get Hahn
to lie to the grand jury about his financial dealings and that he
filed a false 1986 income tax return.
