proceedings. After the sentencing, he kissed his wife goodbye and
was escorted to the county jail in handcuffs by sheriff's deputies.
   About 150 members of Profeta's Full Gospel Tabernacle Church
came to Albany on a bus to watch the sentencing. Before the
proceedings began, Profeta strolled around the courtroom, shaking
hands with and greeting his parishioners.
